'''Mother's Touch''' DWRV 98.3&nbsp;MHz [[Naga City, Camarines Sur|Naga City]]) is a music [[FM broadcasting|FM]] station owned by [[Catholic Media Network]] & [[Radio Veritas-Global Broadcasting Corporation]]. The station's [[studio]] is located at Naga City, Camarines Sur.
==DWRV - FM History== * First broadcast as '''DWRV-FM'''. * In 1998, change to '''Spirit FM'''. * By 2005, change to '''Mother's Touch'''.
